Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3-all, python3-setuptools, python3-sphinx <!nodoc>, python3-sphinx-notfound-page <!nodoc>, python3-sphinx-rtd-theme <!nodoc>
Description: Utilities for filesystem exploration and automated builds This package is particular useful when exploring a filesystem on a remote host, where queries such as "what is the root of the filesystem?", "what is the user's name?", and "what login shell is preferred?" become essential in allowing a remote user to function as if they were logged in locally. . pox is part of pathos, a Python framework for heterogeneous computing.
